data.description: PRICE DROP! Motivated Seller!! Beautiful Home! 4bed/3bath/2car WITH a Swimming Pool! Wood tile, updated electrical, updated plumbing, new garbage disposal, new gutters, newer stove, refrigerator, washer, and dryer stay with acceptable offer! Extra tall privacy fence is SUCH a plus! Close to Cassidy Center Neighborhood WalMart, CVS, Walgreens, and the Northside YMCA; just down the street from Hefner Parkway, hospitals, and schools. Come see this jewel in this picturesque neighborhood.
